    "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nWhile addressing the deprecation, I encountered a crash in the application when attempting to add notes. This issue arises if a note is deleted, but for some reason, the associated note file is not deleted at that time.\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/c56032f0-7382-47a9-8539-5e67f2a1162e\r\n\r\nMy note file is not deleted because of any reason.\r\n\r\n![Screenshot_2023-05-31-18-30-34-341_com google android documentsui](https://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/43d088d1-eafb-4079-b25f-9fe36c82fb57)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nIt should not crash, whether the file is deleted or not.\r\n\r\n**Environment**\r\n- Version of Kiwix Android: 3.7.0 \r\n- Device: Redmi Note 9\r\n- OS version: Android 12\r\n\r\n**Logs**\r\n```\r\nE/AndroidRuntime: FATAL EXCEPTION: main\r\n    Process: org.kiwix.kiwixmobile, PID: 3460\r\n    java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException: setSpan (-1 ... -1) starts before 0\r\n        at android.text.SpannableStringBuilder.checkRange(SpannableStringBuilder.java:1331)\r\n        at android.text.SpannableStringBuilder.setSpan(SpannableStringBuilder.java:685)\r\n        at android.text.SpannableStringBuilder.setSpan(SpannableStringBuilder.java:677)\r\n        at android.text.Selection.setSelection(Selection.java:94)\r\n        at android.text.Selection.setSelection(Selection.java:78)\r\n        at android.text.Selection.setSelection(Selection.java:153)\r\n        at android.widget.EditText.setSelection(EditText.java:135)\r\n        at org.kiwix.kiwixmobile.core.main.AddNoteDialog.readNoteFromFile(AddNoteDialog.kt:413)\r\n        at org.kiwix.kiwixmobile.core.main.AddNoteDialog.displayNote(AddNoteDialog.kt:402)\r\n        at org.kiwix.kiwixmobile.core.main.AddNoteDialog.onViewCreated(AddNoteDialog.kt:275)\r\n        at androidx.fragment.app.Fragment.performViewCreated(Fragment.java:3128)\r\n        at androidx.fragment.app.FragmentStateManager.createView(FragmentStateManager.java:552)\r\n        at androidx.fragment.app.FragmentStateManager.moveToExpectedState(FragmentStateManager.java:261)\r\n        at androidx.fragment.app.FragmentManager.executeOpsTogether(FragmentManager.java:1899)\r\n        at androidx.fragment.app.FragmentManager.removeRedundantOperationsAndExecute(FragmentManager.java:1817)\r\n        at androidx.fragment.app.FragmentManager.execPendingActions(FragmentManager.java:1760)\r\n        at androidx.fragment.app.FragmentManager$5.run(FragmentManager.java:547)\r\n        at android.os.Handler.handleCallback(Handler.java:938)\r\n        at android.os.Handler.dispatchMessage(Handler.java:99)\r\n        at android.os.Looper.loopOnce(Looper.java:210)\r\n        at android.os.Looper.loop(Looper.java:299)\r\n        at android.app.ActivityThread.main(ActivityThread.java:8280)\r\n        at java.lang.reflect.Method.invoke(Native Method)\r\n        at com.android.internal.os.RuntimeInit$MethodAndArgsCaller.run(RuntimeInit.java:576)\r\n        at com.android.internal.os.ZygoteInit.main(ZygoteInit.java:1073)\r\n```\r\n",
